{
  "video_id": "TSomH3iGgYY",
  "title": "Why doctors are offering free tax prep in their waiting rooms | Lucy Marcil",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12987.0,
      "end_time": 16406.0,
      "text": "How many of you have had your doctor ask you about sex?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16820.0,
      "end_time": 18455.0,
      "text": "Your mental health?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18479.0,
      "end_time": 19747.0,
      "text": "Alcohol use?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19772.0,
      "end_time": 22866.0,
      "text": "These questions are almost universal."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22891.0,
      "end_time": 27436.0,
      "text": "But how many of you have had your doctor ask you about money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27461.0,
      "end_time": 28913.0,
      "text": "Most of us haven't."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29609.0,
      "end_time": 33898.0,
      "text": "But that is strange, because compared to most high-income countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33922.0,
      "end_time": 38980.0,
      "text": "child poverty is an epidemic in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38122.0,
      "end_time": 42192.0,
      "text": "It creates conditions that may elevate stress hormone levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42216.0,
      "end_time": 44324.0,
      "text": "and impair brain development."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44879.0,
      "end_time": 50391.0,
      "text": "Poor children in the US are one and a half times more likely to die"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50416.0,
      "end_time": 52977.0,
      "text": "and twice as likely to be hospitalized"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53200.0,
      "end_time": 55320.0,
      "text": "as their middle-class counterparts."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55968.0,
      "end_time": 62726.0,
      "text": "So my colleague Dr. Michael Hole and I started asking moms about money."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63123.0,
      "end_time": 67277.0,
      "text": "We knew we needed to reimagine what a doctor's visit looks like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67301.0,
      "end_time": 68919.0,
      "text": "to get kids out of poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68943.0,
      "end_time": 72484.0,
      "text": "and to give them a fair shot at a healthy life."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73195.0,
      "end_time": 76547.0,
      "text": "Our questions led to a surprising solution:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76572.0,
      "end_time": 77915.0,
      "text": "tax credits."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77939.0,
      "end_time": 82469.0,
      "text": "It turns out, the earned income tax credit, or EITC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82493.0,
      "end_time": 86259.0,
      "text": "is the best poverty prescription we have in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86671.0,
      "end_time": 90638.0,
      "text": "The average mom gets two to three thousand dollars a year from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91600.0,
      "end_time": 94535.0,
      "text": "When families get it, moms and babies are healthier:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94559.0,
      "end_time": 96432.0,
      "text": "fewer depressed moms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96456.0,
      "end_time": 98428.0,
      "text": "babies weighing more at birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98900.0,
      "end_time": 103244.0,
      "text": "But one out of five families who could get it doesn't,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 103268.0,
      "end_time": 106929.0,
      "text": "and most who do lose of hundreds of dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106953.0,
      "end_time": 109837.0,
      "text": "to the for-profit tax-preparation industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 111409.0,
      "end_time": 115730.0,
      "text": "One day, a mom asked us why we couldn't do her taxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115970.0,
      "end_time": 116693.0,
      "text": "while she waited for the doctor."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116717.0,
      "end_time": 117726.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117750.0,
      "end_time": 121994.0,
      "text": "We all know that purgatory. Why not make good use of that time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122180.0,
      "end_time": 124780.0,
      "text": "So we started StreetCred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 124102.0,
      "end_time": 129280.0,
      "text": "an organization prescribing tax preparation in clinics serving kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129674.0,
      "end_time": 131729.0,
      "text": "This is a brand-new approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131753.0,
      "end_time": 135780.0,
      "text": "and one that left some questioning our sanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135103.0,
      "end_time": 137875.0,
      "text": "After all, we're doctors, not accountants."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 137899.0,
      "end_time": 141415.0,
      "text": "But we have something accountants don't:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141439.0,
      "end_time": 143528.0,
      "text": "access to families."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144750.0,
      "end_time": 149330.0,
      "text": "Over 90 percent of kids in the US see a doctor at least once a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 149732.0,
      "end_time": 151172.0,
      "text": "Their parents trust us"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 151196.0,
      "end_time": 154725.0,
      "text": "and will do anything to give them a better life."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 156207.0,
      "end_time": 160186.0,
      "text": "Doctors in every clinic around the country could be doing this work, too --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 160210.0,
      "end_time": 161574.0,
      "text": "it's simple, really."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 162126.0,
      "end_time": 164855.0,
      "text": "The hospital registers as a tax-preparation site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 164879.0,
      "end_time": 168614.0,
      "text": "and everyone, from medical students to retirees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168639.0,
      "end_time": 173390.0,
      "text": "can volunteer as a tax preparer after passing an IRS exam."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 173905.0,
      "end_time": 176656.0,
      "text": "It's not as hard as it sounds, I promise."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 176680.0,
      "end_time": 179766.0,
      "text": "I certainly never thought I would be doing other people's taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 179790.0,
      "end_time": 181149.0,
      "text": "but here I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 181823.0,
      "end_time": 184698.0,
      "text": "We're nearing the end of our third year."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 185770.0,
      "end_time": 189784.0,
      "text": "In the first two, we returned 1.6 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 189808.0,
      "end_time": 192921.0,
      "text": "to 750 families in Boston alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 192945.0,
      "end_time": 194131.0,
      "text": "This year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 194155.0,
      "end_time": 198150.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 199106.0,
      "end_time": 202897.0,
      "text": "This year, we've expanded to nine sites in four states."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 203357.0,
      "end_time": 208520.0,
      "text": "Sixty-three percent of our families have never heard of the EITC."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 208968.0,
      "end_time": 212146.0,
      "text": "How can you claim something you haven't heard of?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 212170.0,
      "end_time": 215113.0,
      "text": "And half have never used free tax preparation."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 215769.0,
      "end_time": 218344.0,
      "text": "That two to three thousand dollars a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 218368.0,
      "end_time": 220234.0,
      "text": "goes a long way."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 220259.0,
      "end_time": 221428.0,
      "text": "Take hunger."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 221984.0,
      "end_time": 226562.0,
      "text": "An adequately nutritious, low-cost diet for a mom and two young kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 226586.0,
      "end_time": 229546.0,
      "text": "costs 477 dollars a month."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 230650.0,
      "end_time": 234195.0,
      "text": "With EITC money, that family can eat for five to six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234830.0,
      "end_time": 236938.0,
      "text": "Or think about medical care."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 236962.0,
      "end_time": 240945.0,
      "text": "Twenty million children in the US lack access to care"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 240969.0,
      "end_time": 243102.0,
      "text": "meeting modern pediatric standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 244122.0,
      "end_time": 250532.0,
      "text": "And yet, the average cost of that care is only 400 dollars per kid per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 251157.0,
      "end_time": 254739.0,
      "text": "EITC money can help fix this access problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 255755.0,
      "end_time": 257837.0,
      "text": "Perhaps most powerfully of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 257861.0,
      "end_time": 259582.0,
      "text": "this money gives moms hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 260510.0,
      "end_time": 264482.0,
      "text": "One mom used her refund for her son to study abroad in Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 265133.0,
      "end_time": 267489.0,
      "text": "She was struggling to pay her rent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 267513.0,
      "end_time": 271310.0,
      "text": "but she saw EITC money as his shot at a better future."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 272640.0,
      "end_time": 273948.0,
      "text": "We have an opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273972.0,
      "end_time": 276454.0,
      "text": "as doctors and as citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 276478.0,
      "end_time": 278645.0,
      "text": "to get to the root of this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 278669.0,
      "end_time": 280340.0,
      "text": "We can reimagine health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280364.0,
      "end_time": 284370.0,
      "text": "as a place addressing the causes of poor health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 284610.0,
      "end_time": 285705.0,
      "text": "be it infections"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285730.0,
      "end_time": 287138.0,
      "text": "or finances."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 287567.0,
      "end_time": 288778.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288802.0,
      "end_time": 294582.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}